Also known as the 'heritage city', Mysore has beautiful palaces and many other attractions tourists can explore.

HolidayIQ Traveller Zain says, “Mysore is called the city of Palaces. The main places to visit are : Mysore Palace (Sunday because light is available only on sunday). Brindavan Garden, Srirangapatna (Tipu Sultans Legacy), Chamundi Hill, Karanji Lake, Sand & Wax Museum, Zoo Garden (Very Big) and St. Philomena's Church.”

